\li{\strong{Breached credentials}: Check paste sites, breach databases. Credential}
\li{\strong{Social media}: Employee roles, org charts, technology stack, office photos}
\li{\strong{Public records}: Domain registrations, DNS records, job postings (reveal}
\li{\strong{Code repositories}: Leaked secrets, internal URLs, employee emails in}
\li{\strong{Metadata}: Document metadata (author names, software versions, internal}
}
}

